<h2>Publish Original Research and Data</h2>
<p>Original data is the single fastest path to AI citability. AI models prefer to cite primary sources over summaries of other people's research. When you publish a stat that no one else has, every AI model that encounters it must cite you as the source.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="AI citation statistics for brands showing citation rates across ChatGPT Perplexity and Google AI Overviews" src="/images/blog/ai-citation-statistics-brands.webp" /></p>
