<h3>Build Digital PR That AI Models Can Find</h3>
<p>Every media mention is a brand signal that AI models weigh when deciding what to cite. But not all mentions are equal. A quote in a Forbes article with your name and brand linked carries more weight than a passing mention in a no-name blog.</p>
<p>Focus your <a href="/glossary/digital-pr/">digital PR</a> efforts on:</p>
<ul>
<li>Publishing guest columns with original data in industry publications</li>
<li>Getting quoted as a subject matter expert in news articles</li>
<li>Contributing to annual reports, surveys, and industry roundups</li>
<li>Earning mentions on podcasts that publish show notes with links</li>
</ul>
