<ul>
<li>Does your brand appear in the response?</li>
<li>Are you cited with a link, or just mentioned by name?</li>
<li>What position is your citation (first source, third, fifth)?</li>
<li>Which competitor brands appear alongside yours?</li>
</ul>
<p>Run this audit monthly. Document the results in a spreadsheet. Track changes over time.</p>
